---
import HeritageLayout from '../layouts/HeritageLayout.astro';
---
<HeritageLayout
  title="Support Heritage — Yemen Architecture Initiative"
  description="Support the documentation and conservation of Yemen's architectural heritage."
  eyebrow="Support"
  eyebrowAr="ادعم التراث"
  accent="#B45309"
  heading="Support heritage"
  headingAr="ادعم التراث"
>
  <p class="lede en-only">A way to support YAI's documentation and conservation work is being prepared. Thank you for your interest in protecting Yemen's built heritage.</p>
  <p class="lede ar-only ar-text">تُجهَّز حالياً وسيلة لدعم عمل المبادرة في التوثيق والحفظ. شكراً لاهتمامك بحماية التراث المبني في اليمن.</p>
  <p class="cross-ref"><a href="/"><span class="en-only">Back to home →</span><span class="ar-only ar-text">العودة للرئيسية ←</span></a></p>
  <style>
    .lede { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); max-width: 52ch; }
    .cross-ref { margin-top: 2rem; } .cross-ref a { color: var(--accent); }
  </style>
</HeritageLayout>
